<span class="main-color"><b>Dakewe group</b></span>
 was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Shenzhen. Our business involves in self-developed histology equipment and scientific research reagents.
</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Dakewe group has more than 14 branches based both in China and overseas, including Beijing, Shanghai, Hong Kong, USA, Europe and India, and more.
</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
Meanwhile, Dakewe is consistently complementing the service and distribution network to provide quality products and service to customers all around the world. Dakewe products have been sold to more than 60 countries/regions and served more than 10000 users.
</p>',null,'Syntec Scientific','http://en.dakewemedical.com/','Dakewe/Dakewe-logo.png',null,'Dakewe/Dakewe-logo_400x267.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'05-JAN-25',null,'_Dakewe','assets/images/Backgrounds/Lab_14_opaque.png','width:90px;');
INSERT INTO syntec_suppliers_staging_v2 (DELETED,ACTIVE,SUPPLIER_ID,SUPPLIER_NAME,SHORT_NAME,CLASS_ID,CLASS_COLOUR,PROFILE_1,PROFILE_2,BUSINESS,WEBSITE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_SMALL,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_1,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_2,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_3,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_4,ADDRESS_1,ADDRESS_2,ADDRESS_3,ADDRESS_4,ADDRESS_5,DATE_CREATED,DATE_DELETED,ANCHOR_ID,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_BACKGROUND,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE_SCALE_SMALLER) VALUES ('N','Y','SUP-0002','Atom Scientific',null,null,'#E50E17','<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
<span class="main-color"><b>Atom Scientific</b></span>
 is a leading UK Manufacturer of IVDR Diagnostic Stains & Reagents, Chemicals, Volumetrics, Buffer Solutions, supported by an extensive range of consumables from leading brands.
</p>




<p class="heading-desc t-justify">We offer Simple and Reliable Solutions for Science, servicing customers in over 60 countries throughout the world.
</p>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">We aim to make our customers experience, friendly, efficient, and focused on their needs.
</p>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Based in Manchester UK, we manufacture, pack, and ship a comprehensive range of IVD-R Diagnostic Stains, Reagents, Chemicals, High Purity Solvents, Standards, Buffers and Volumetric Solutions.</p>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">In addition to our own manufactured products Atom Scientific also distribute a wide range of laboratory consumables, glassware, and equipment to meet our customer needs.
</p>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Our friendly team is dedicated to ensuring our customers have a simple and pleasant experience, supported by industry leading standards of quality.</p>',null,'Syntec Scientific','https://atomscientific.com/','Atom/Atom-logo.png',null,'Atom/Atom-logo_400x267.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'05-JAN-25',null,'_Atom','assets/images/Backgrounds/Lab_6_opaque.png','width:90px;');
INSERT INTO syntec_suppliers_staging_v2 (DELETED,ACTIVE,SUPPLIER_ID,SUPPLIER_NAME,SHORT_NAME,CLASS_ID,CLASS_COLOUR,PROFILE_1,PROFILE_2,BUSINESS,WEBSITE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_SMALL,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_1,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_2,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_3,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_4,ADDRESS_1,ADDRESS_2,ADDRESS_3,ADDRESS_4,ADDRESS_5,DATE_CREATED,DATE_DELETED,ANCHOR_ID,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_BACKGROUND,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE_SCALE_SMALLER) VALUES ('N','Y','SUP-0008','Medi Diagnostics',null,null,'#932780','<p class="heading-desc t-justify"><span style="font-size: 24pt; color: #93277f; font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif;"><strong>Our Operation</strong></span></p>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify"><span ><span class="main-color"><b>Medi-Diagnostic</b></span> is a company fully operated by an experience team of&nbsp; Technical and Radiological Imaging Sales and Marketing as well as Technical Service Personnel with well over 25 years of experience and knowledge in this industry.</span></p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify"><span style="font-size: 24pt; color: #93277f; font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif;"><strong>Business Strengths</strong></span></p>


<ul class="ullist">
<li><span class="heading-desc t-justify">Established branch network within Malaysia with excellent integrated services of sales, distribution, logistics and technical support.</span><br></li>
<li><span class="heading-desc t-justify">Our competent and well-trained field team work closely with our customers; thus understanding our customers’ needs and requirements and thereby able to service them better.(Slide Gambar Tangan)</span><br></li>
<li><span class="heading-desc t-justify">Our ability to remain flexible allows us to adapt well to the ever-changing market forces. This enables us to constantly evolve and continuously add value to the services we provide to our clients.</span><br></li>
</ul>


<p class="heading-desc t-justify"><span style="font-size: 24pt; color: #93277f; font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif;"><strong>What We Do</strong></span></p>
<p  class="heading-desc t-justify"><span >We provide our customers with a total solution concept to meet their technical and radiological imaging requirements. Our services include the trading, marketing, sales, distribution and technical services needs of our clients; starting with pre-sales consultancy, deliveries till after-market sales and services.</span></p>',null,'Syntec Scientific','https://medi-diagnostic.com/','Medi-Diagnostic/Medi-Diagnostic-logo.png',null,'Medi-Diagnostic/Medi-Diagnostic-logo_400x267.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'05-JAN-25',null,'_Medi','assets/images/Backgrounds/Lab_7_opaque.png','width:120px;');
INSERT INTO syntec_suppliers_staging_v2 (DELETED,ACTIVE,SUPPLIER_ID,SUPPLIER_NAME,SHORT_NAME,CLASS_ID,CLASS_COLOUR,PROFILE_1,PROFILE_2,BUSINESS,WEBSITE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_SMALL,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_1,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_2,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_3,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_4,ADDRESS_1,ADDRESS_2,ADDRESS_3,ADDRESS_4,ADDRESS_5,DATE_CREATED,DATE_DELETED,ANCHOR_ID,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_BACKGROUND,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE_SCALE_SMALLER) VALUES ('N','Y','SUP-0015','Bio Diagnostics',null,null,'#9A0602','<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Established in 1979, <span class="main-color"><b>Bio-Diagnostics</b></span>
 is privately owned, rapidly growing, UK bio-tech business, based 40 miles south west of Birmingham, UK.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Bio-Diagnostics is highly regarded and trusted globally, working closely with partners providing, Distribution, Medical Logistics, Contract Manufacture, (including final kit assembly and cartoning), Contract R&D, Laboratory Services, sample processing and testing.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Operating from a complete UK registered facility, providing a fully regulated address for certification requirements post Brexit to third parties.</p>


<ul class="ullist">
<li><span class="heading-desc t-justify">Distribution – A Distributor of Medical products for third parties</span><br></li>
<li><span class="heading-desc t-justify">Medical Logistics – Provider of Medical Logistics to third parties for global despatch and transportation of their products</span><br></li>
<li><span class="heading-desc t-justify">Manufacture – GMP certified for own and contract manufactured healthcare products, IVDs, and associated medical products</span><br></li>

<li><span class="heading-desc t-justify">Laboratory Services and testing. – Provider of clinical laboratory services to third parties who require use of a fully certified and regulated facility for the testing of patient samples. ISO30485 accredited laboratory.</span><br></li>
<li><span class="heading-desc t-justify">UK registered fully regulated address for certification requirements post Brexit to third parties.</span><br></li>
<li><span class="heading-desc t-justify">As the longest established Autoimmune company in the UK, our expertise in immunology has enabled rapid establishment as the clear market leader in many aspects of Allergy testing as well as treatments in the UK.</span><br></li>


</ul>


<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Bio-Diagnostics now has 4 main divisions in Immunology, Immunohistochemistry and Dermatology, and Allergy and continues to work with commercial and academic entities on projects to take a concept through to commercial products.</p>',null,'Syntec Scientific','https://biodiagnostics.co.uk/','Bio_Diagnostics/Bio_Diagnostics-logo.png',null,'Bio_Diagnostics/Bio_Diagnostics-logo_400x267.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'05-JAN-25',null,'_BioDiagnostics','assets/images/Backgrounds/Lab_8_opaque.png','width:90px;');
INSERT INTO syntec_suppliers_staging_v2 (DELETED,ACTIVE,SUPPLIER_ID,SUPPLIER_NAME,SHORT_NAME,CLASS_ID,CLASS_COLOUR,PROFILE_1,PROFILE_2,BUSINESS,WEBSITE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_SMALL,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_1,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_2,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_3,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_4,ADDRESS_1,ADDRESS_2,ADDRESS_3,ADDRESS_4,ADDRESS_5,DATE_CREATED,DATE_DELETED,ANCHOR_ID,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_BACKGROUND,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE_SCALE_SMALLER) VALUES ('N','Y','SUP-0017','Cerillo',null,null,'#F6CB4A','<div class="heading side-head">

<h3 class="heavy-font">The Cellular Analytics Solutions Company</h3>

</div>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">For industry researchers, <span class="main-color"><b>Cerillo</b></span> is the visionary partner in cellular analytics, uniting data generation and intelligent computational biology to maximize research potential and drive rapid discoveries.</p>


<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Our application-agnostic platform (hardware, software, and intelligence) generates and transforms biologically and environmentally relevant data into research insights using scalable intelligent computational models.</p>


<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Cerillo’s Research Platform is equipped with state-of-the-art features designed to enhance your research capabilities. Real-time data visualization allows for immediate insight into experimental progress, while remote monitoring ensures you can oversee your experiments from anywhere. The platform’s scalable connectivity supports multiple microplate readers, offering the flexibility to expand as your research grows. From microbiome research to drug discovery and bioprocessing, Cerillo’s versatile platform ensures consistent, reliable outcomes across diverse scientific fields.</p>',null,'Syntec Scientific','https://cerillo.bio/','Cerillo/Cerillo-logo.png',null,'Cerillo/Cerillo-logo_400x267.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'05-JAN-25',null,'_Cerillo','assets/images/Backgrounds/Lab_10_opaque.png','width:80px;');
INSERT INTO syntec_suppliers_staging_v2 (DELETED,ACTIVE,SUPPLIER_ID,SUPPLIER_NAME,SHORT_NAME,CLASS_ID,CLASS_COLOUR,PROFILE_1,PROFILE_2,BUSINESS,WEBSITE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_SMALL,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_1,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_2,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_3,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_4,ADDRESS_1,ADDRESS_2,ADDRESS_3,ADDRESS_4,ADDRESS_5,DATE_CREATED,DATE_DELETED,ANCHOR_ID,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_BACKGROUND,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE_SCALE_SMALLER) VALUES ('N','Y','SUP-0028','Flash Dx',null,null,'#4D81B3','<p class="heading-desc t-justify"><span class="main-color"><b>FlashDx</b></span>  is an innovative molecular diagnostics company focused on delivering rapid, multiplexed, sample-to-answer testing systems for decentralized and point-of-care settings. Their flagship platform, the sSPRT™ System, leverages a proprietary semi-solid phase real-time PCR technology to provide accurate, high-throughput testing with minimal hands-on time. Designed for use in hospitals, clinics, and near-patient environments, FlashDx aims to transform the speed and accessibility of molecular diagnostics without compromising quality or clinical performance.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">With a growing test menu that includes respiratory panels, GI pathogens, STIs, and Group B Streptococcus (GBS), FlashDx supports flexible syndromic testing using compact, cartridge-based workflows. Their CE-IVDR-certified systems are built for efficiency—enabling random access, modular scalability (4T, 8T, or 12T), and results in under an hour. By combining high-multiplex capability with intuitive software, FlashDx delivers clinically actionable insights faster, helping healthcare providers respond rapidly to infectious disease threats.</p>',null,'Syntec Scientific','https://www.flash-dx.com/','FlashDx/FlashDx-logo.png',null,'FlashDx/FlashDx-logo_400x267.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'05-JAN-25',null,'_FlashDx','assets/images/Backgrounds/Lab_50_opaque.png','width:80px;');
INSERT INTO syntec_suppliers_staging_v2 (DELETED,ACTIVE,SUPPLIER_ID,SUPPLIER_NAME,SHORT_NAME,CLASS_ID,CLASS_COLOUR,PROFILE_1,PROFILE_2,BUSINESS,WEBSITE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_SMALL,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_1,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_2,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_3,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_4,ADDRESS_1,ADDRESS_2,ADDRESS_3,ADDRESS_4,ADDRESS_5,DATE_CREATED,DATE_DELETED,ANCHOR_ID,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_BACKGROUND,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE_SCALE_SMALLER) VALUES ('N','Y','SUP-0005','Diatech',null,null,'#013674','<p class="heading-desc t-justify"><span class="main-color"><b>Diatech Pharmacogenetics</b></span>
 is the Italian leader in the development, production and commercialisation of pharmacogenetics tests for cancer precision medicine.
Founded in 1996, Diatech Pharmacogenetics has sustained constant organic growth over the years and now owns more than 70% of the Italian molecular diagnostic market and it is rapidly growing worldwide; to date, more than 20.000 diagnostic tests have been performed using its solutions and every year Diatech Pharmacogenetics reinvests 20% of it revenues in R&D.
Diatech Pharmacogenetics is able to take pharmacogenetics tests from idea to market on a variety of platforms, from real-time PCR to barcoded microarrays, mass-spectrometry and next generation sequencing, supplying all reagents, instruments, materials and support necessary. Its complete solutions guide diagnostic operators from sample extraction, quality control, molecular assay to bioinformatic analysis and report.
</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
The latest products launched include a liquid biopsy cfDNA extraction kit, a real-time PCR system with all reagent provided in a dry and stable format, micro-satellite instability assays and an end-to-end NGS solution that works on both Illumina and IonTorrent platforms.
</p>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
All Diatech products are developed under EN ISO 9001 and EN ISO 13485 and have been designed, developed and validated in accordance with the Regulation (EU) 2017/746 on in vitro diagnostic medical devices (CE-IVD).
</p>',null,'Syntec Scientific','https://www.diatechpharmacogenetics.com/en/','Diatech/Diatech-logo.png',null,'Diatech/Diatech-logo_400x267.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'05-JAN-25',null,'_Diatech','assets/images/Backgrounds/Lab_15_opaque.png','width:120px;');
INSERT INTO syntec_suppliers_staging_v2 (DELETED,ACTIVE,SUPPLIER_ID,SUPPLIER_NAME,SHORT_NAME,CLASS_ID,CLASS_COLOUR,PROFILE_1,PROFILE_2,BUSINESS,WEBSITE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_SMALL,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_1,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_2,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_3,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_4,ADDRESS_1,ADDRESS_2,ADDRESS_3,ADDRESS_4,ADDRESS_5,DATE_CREATED,DATE_DELETED,ANCHOR_ID,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_BACKGROUND,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE_SCALE_SMALLER) VALUES ('N','Y','SUP-0006','Medite',null,null,'#E64435','<div class="tab-pane active" id="about-Medite">

                               <h4 class="centered main-color uppercase">Cancer Diagnostics</h4>

                               <p class="heading-desc t-justify">Earlier and
                                    more accurate detection combined with better monitoring of cancer or pre-cancer
                                    conditions is increasing the patients chance to survive this serious health
                                    condition. Our team of highly qualified researchers and engineers is working on
                                    solutions realizing that goal.</p>
                                <h4 class="centered main-color">INSTRUMENTS AND SUPPLIES</h4>
                                <p class="heading-desc t-justify">Your one stop shop
                                    for histology and cytology laboratories with the complete set of innovative,
                                    German engineered instruments and highest quality and cost effective supply
                                    products. Savings through cost effective products and increasing automation will
                                    support your success.</p>
                                <h4 class="centered main-color">DIAGNOSTICS MARKET</h4>
                                <p class="heading-desc t-justify">The incidence of cancer
                                    is expecting to rise a further 57 % in the next two decades. The Company is
                                    emerging as rapidly growing disruptive force in the multi-billion dollar global
                                    histology and cytology systems marketplace while positioned to build significant
                                    shareholder value.</p>
</div>',null,'Syntec Scientific','https://infrico.com/en/','medite/medite-logo.png',null,'medite/medite-logo_400x267.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'05-JAN-25',null,'_Medite','assets/images/Backgrounds/Lab_8_opaque.png','width:80px;');
INSERT INTO syntec_suppliers_staging_v2 (DELETED,ACTIVE,SUPPLIER_ID,SUPPLIER_NAME,SHORT_NAME,CLASS_ID,CLASS_COLOUR,PROFILE_1,PROFILE_2,BUSINESS,WEBSITE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_SMALL,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_1,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_2,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_3,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_4,ADDRESS_1,ADDRESS_2,ADDRESS_3,ADDRESS_4,ADDRESS_5,DATE_CREATED,DATE_DELETED,ANCHOR_ID,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_BACKGROUND,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE_SCALE_SMALLER) VALUES ('N','Y','SUP-0011','Trajan',null,null,'#AD172B','<div class="syn_text-block">
  <div class="syn_visible-part">
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">
			<b>The world of analytical and medical science is on a journey – from laboratory to sample source and ultimately into the home, informing the individual.</b>
			</p>
			<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Trajan aspires to bring together a range of global businesses in the fields of scientific and medical analysis that have a common bond; that they each service this direction in some way.
			</p>
</div>
	  <div class="syn_toggle-icon">
		<i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
	  </div>
	  
	  
  <div class="syn_show-more-start">	  
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Our focus is on developing and commercializing technologies that enable analytical systems to be more selective, sensitive and specific for biological, environmental or food related measurements especially those that can lead to portability, miniaturization and affordability.
</p>
<p class="heading-desc t-justify">Our vision revolves around partnerships: development partnerships to invest in leading technologies and commercial partnerships to deliver breakthrough solutions to the world.
</p>
  </div>
</div>',null,'Syntec Scientific','https://www.trajanscimed.com/','trajan/trajan-logo.png',null,'trajan/trajan-logo_400x267.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'05-JAN-25',null,'_Trajan','assets/images/Backgrounds/Lab_14_opaque.png','width:60px;');
INSERT INTO syntec_suppliers_staging_v2 (DELETED,ACTIVE,SUPPLIER_ID,SUPPLIER_NAME,SHORT_NAME,CLASS_ID,CLASS_COLOUR,PROFILE_1,PROFILE_2,BUSINESS,WEBSITE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_SMALL,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_1,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_2,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_3,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_4,ADDRESS_1,ADDRESS_2,ADDRESS_3,ADDRESS_4,ADDRESS_5,DATE_CREATED,DATE_DELETED,ANCHOR_ID,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_BACKGROUND,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE_SCALE_SMALLER) VALUES ('N','Y','SUP-0026','ARCTIKO',null,null,'#7EBC42','<p class="heading-desc t-justify"><span class="main-color"><b>ARCTIKO</b></span> is a Danish company specializing in advanced cold storage solutions tailored for the medical, pharmaceutical, and laboratory industries. Known for its precision engineering and reliable performance, ARCTIKO offers a wide range of freezers, refrigerators, and ultra-low temperature (ULT) systems designed to ensure the safe storage of sensitive biological samples and vaccines. With a focus on user-centric design, energy efficiency, and global regulatory compliance, ARCTIKO’s products are trusted by hospitals, research institutions, and laboratories worldwide.</p>

<p class="heading-desc t-justify">The company combines Scandinavian innovation with robust manufacturing standards to deliver reliable and eco-friendly solutions. Whether for blood banks, biobanks, or clinical diagnostics, ARCTIKO''s offerings—ranging from compact countertop units to high-capacity ULT freezers—support critical cold chain applications. Their dedication to sustainability and digital integration (e.g., smart monitoring, remote alerts) positions ARCTIKO as a forward-thinking partner in modern biomedical cold storage.</p>',null,'Syntec Scientific','http://www.arctiko.com/','arctiko/arctiko-logo.png',null,'arctiko/arctik-logo_400x267.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'05-JAN-25',null,'_Arctiko','assets/images/images_misc/Lab_96_opaque.png','width:80px;');
INSERT INTO syntec_suppliers_staging_v2 (DELETED,ACTIVE,SUPPLIER_ID,SUPPLIER_NAME,SHORT_NAME,CLASS_ID,CLASS_COLOUR,PROFILE_1,PROFILE_2,BUSINESS,WEBSITE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE,SUPPLIER_LOGO_SMALL,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_1,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_2,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_3,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_4,ADDRESS_1,ADDRESS_2,ADDRESS_3,ADDRESS_4,ADDRESS_5,DATE_CREATED,DATE_DELETED,ANCHOR_ID,SUPPLIER_IMAGE_BACKGROUND,SUPPLIER_LOGO_LARGE_SCALE_SMALLER) VALUES ('N','Y','SUP-0009','Optra Scan',null,null,'#62C530','<p class="heading-desc t-justify"><span class="main-color"><b>OptraSCAN</b></span> is a pioneering digital pathology company, with various patents on its automatic scanning device technology coupled with tumor and immune cell intelligent scoring systems, dedicated to transforming the future of pathology services through advanced digital slide scanners & AI-driven solutions. We empower healthcare institutions to transition from traditional microscopes to digital pathology for improved diagnostics*, research, & education. Our innovative technologies, offer high-speed, precise imaging & analysis that streamline lab workflows, enhance diagnostic* accuracy & improve patient outcomes.</p>',null,'Syntec Scientific','https://www.optrascan.com/','OptraScan/OptraScan-logo.png',null,'OptraScan/OptraScan-logo_400x267.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,'05-JAN-25',null,'_Optra','assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/OptraScan/Background_opaque.png','width:90px;');
