Qilta Sport® is a pioneering brand dedicated to enhancing athletic recovery and performance through innovative post-activity solutions. Specializing in scientifically developed recovery garments and protocols, Qilta Sport® helps athletes accelerate muscle recovery, reduce inflammation, and minimize downtime after intense training or competition. Designed with input from sports scientists, physiotherapists, and elite athletes, Qilta Sport® products provide targeted support to optimize recovery and keep athletes performing at their peak.
